By: Sri Ramakrishna
---
I used to go into samâdhi uttering the word ‘Mâ’. While repeating the
word I would draw the Mother of the Universe to me, as it were, like the
fishermen casting their net and after a while drawing it in. When they draw
in the net they find big fish inside it.
